ZH: 我每天喝一瓶矿泉水。
EN: I drink a bottle of mineral water every day.

ZH: 你可以买一些矿泉水吗？
EN: Can you buy some mineral water?

ZH: 这个矿泉水很好喝。
EN: This mineral water tastes good.

ZH: 矿泉水对身体很有好处。
EN: Mineral water is good for your health.

ZH: 我喜欢喝冷的矿泉水。
EN: I like to drink cold mineral water.

ZH: 请给我一瓶矿泉水。
EN: Please give me a bottle of mineral water.

ZH: 这个超市有很多种矿泉水。
EN: This supermarket has many kinds of mineral water.

ZH: 矿泉水可以帮助消化。
EN: Mineral water can help with digestion.

